@startuml
title Factory Method - Ejemplo 1 - Implementacion Generica
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  class ConcreteCreator {
  }
  class ConcreteProduct {
    +name(): String
  }
  abstract class Creator {
  }
  interface Product <<interfaz>> {
  }
}

Creator <|-- ConcreteCreator
Product <|.. ConcreteProduct
ConcreteCreator ..> ConcreteProduct : crea
Creator ..> ConcreteProduct : crea
Product ..> ConcreteProduct : crea
Main ..> ConcreteCreator : ejecuta

note bottom
La implementacion esta concentrada en src/pattern/PatternImplementation.java.
Main solo instancia y ejecuta el caso de uso.
end note
@enduml
